FBIS3-14084 "drnes056_l_94008" FBIS-NES-94-056 Document Type:Daily Report 20 Mar 1994 ISRAEL Court Extends Golan Settler's Detention TA2003080594 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 0700 GMT 20 Mar 94 TA2003080594 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el Language: Hebrew Article Type:BFN [Text] The Nazareth District Court has extended the administrative detention of Mikha'el Ben-Horin, from the settlement of Nov on the Golan Heights, by two months. Our correspondent Yo'av Aviv reports that the defense minister had asked the court for a three-month extension. Several dozen people are currently demonstrating outside the courthouse and carrying placards denouncing the government.
